text: Module 11, Trend Reversal Audit Flow Indicator is our key focus for this entire section and really exciting section looking at the various different types of price ladder strategies that we will be employing in order to determine those critical juncture points where the market is about to turn around after it ends or exhausts one direction in the markets.
